value.name: First Kill
value.overview: Falling in love is tricky for teens Juliette and Calliope: One's a vampire, the other's a vampire hunter — and both are ready to make their first kill.

value.name: My Feet Are Killing Me: First Steps
value.original_name: My Feet Are Killing Me: First Steps
value.overview: Quarantining at home hasn't stopped everyone's favorite foot fixers from helping patients with their foot troubles. Dr. Brad and Dr. Ebonie are teaming up with the compassionate and intelligent Dr. Sarah Haller, who is joining the medical series and has been working alongside Dr. Brad for years, on all new episodes of My Feet Are Killing Me: First Steps. In the midst of a world shutdown by COVID-19, these dynamic foot doctors pledge to help shocking podiatric cases, one video call at a time. Each 30-minute episode will follow three patients as they undergo virtual consultations to begin their journey towards surgeries that will leave their feet radically transformed and their lives changed forever. COVID toes have nothing on these cases!

value.name: The First 48: Killer Confessions
value.overview: The First 48: Killer Confessions continues A&E's First 48 franchise. Old cases are revisited and the Detectives on each case give updates as to their progress.
